"ngram\": \"the most logical\\\" choice\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It ensures that I have a little more time and thus can prepare longer and better,\\\" he said in a statement released by his Alpecin-Deceuninck team.\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little more time\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"his Alpecin-Deceuninck team\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel has won titles in many disciplines and thought at one point about competing in the cross-country mountain bike event at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van der Poel\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"titles\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"many disciplines\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"one point\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 781}, {\"ngram\": \"the cross-country mountain bike event\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he faced what he called a \\\"difficult puzzle to put together\\\" with the route of the road race suiting his skills.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a \\\"difficult puzzle\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"the route\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"his skills\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just the road race?\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Just the road race\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only mountain biking?\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only mountain biking\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or both?\\\"\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"he said.\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whether or not in combination with the Tour de France, which I personally consider the best possible preparation for the Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999999895783276, \"rank\": 6.0345056623022796e-09, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"combination\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"the best possible preparation\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel finally made his decision.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van der Poel\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"his decision\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let us say I chose the most logical thing,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"the most logical thing\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, in consultation with the team, I opted for a slightly longer rest period, after which I can build up to the Tour de France and the Olympic road race without time pressure.\\\"\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999999895783276, \"rank\": 6.0345056623022796e-09, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\"