//dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 29-year-old rider\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"impressive form\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"victories\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tour\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1601}, {\"ngram\": \"his hunt\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"stage wins\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And the goal is to win a stage myself this year,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the goal\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1737}, {\"ngram\": \"a stage\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Last year I got sick when there were a few stages where I had chances.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few stages\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"chances\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully I will be spared from that in this edition.\\\"\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this edition\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel added that wearing the world champion's rainbow jersey this season played a role in his decision to race at the Tour.\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 2042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1965, \"end\": 1979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rainbow_jersey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"rainbow jersey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rainbow_jersey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rainbow_jersey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van der Poel\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"a role\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"his decision\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2021}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tour\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a special year,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a special year\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As world champion I like to ride in that jersey as much as possible.\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"world champion\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"that jersey\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I also prefer not to miss the Tour de France.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2179, \"end\": 2193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999999895783276, \"rank\": 6.0345056623022796e-09, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that proved to be a good preparation last year, then towards the World Championships.\\\"\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good preparation\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also hinted that he could compete in mountain biking at future Olympics.\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mountain biking\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2342}, {\"ngram\": \"future Olympics\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel crashed out of the mountain bike race at the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van der Poel\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2375}, {\"ngram\": \"the mountain bike race\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Who knows what's still possible in 2028 in Los Angeles?\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2482, \"end\": 2493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9986447774993905, \"rank\": 0.0013567307813245504, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's still a long time away, but I will be in a different phase of my career then,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2589, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different phase\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Maybe then I can put everything on that mountain biking.\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"that mountain biking\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year the combination is just too difficult.\\\"\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the combination\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel, who is currently training in Spain, will not compete before the June 29-July 21 Tour de France.\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2742, \"end\": 2747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9885907772665178, \"rank\": 0.008072552667878317, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2793, \"end\": 2807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999999895783276, \"rank\": 6.0345056623022796e-09, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [],